casebody.data:
Brett DAFFRON, Appellant,
v.
Jane DAFFRON, Respondent. WD 81990 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: April 30, 2019 Michael L. Taylor and Jennifer Ray, St. Joseph, MO, Attorneys for Appellants. Katie McClaflin, Overland Park, KS, Attorney for Respondent. Before Division Two: Thomas N. Chapman, Presiding Judge, and Mark D. Pfeiffer and Cynthia L. Martin, Judges

Order

Per Curiam:

Mr. Brett Daffron appeals from the Judgment of the Circuit Court of Andrew County, Missouri, Domestic Division, in favor of Ms. Jane Daffron and denying Mr. Daffron's post-dissolution motion to modify the parenting plan between himself and Ms. Daffron. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, a memorandum of law has been provided to the parties. The judgment is affirmed. Rule 84.16(b).
